 Japanese anime celebrities can’t escape China’s campaign over Taiwan|author=Jane Li|date=2020-10-02|website=[[石英财经网|石英财经网]]|access-date=2020-10-04|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://archive.today/20201003014808/https://qz.com/1911573/virtual-youtubers-suspended-after-calling-taiwan-a-country/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。

